snippet.title: Airspace Defender - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Get a peek at Airspace Defender in this trailer for the upcoming game. Airspace Defender is coming to Meta Quest 2, Meta Quest 3, and Quest Pro, and a demo is available now.
